384
00:26:12,865 --> 00:26:15,159
<font color="#ffff00">HENTIKAN PEMECATAN MASSAL</font>

385
00:26:32,426 --> 00:26:34,095
"Perkumpulan Serikat Buruh"?

386
00:26:35,054 --> 00:26:36,180
Kim Seung-cheol?

387
00:26:44,188 --> 00:26:46,607
Ayah banyak membantu mereka

388
00:26:47,358 --> 00:26:48,818
saat pabrik itu dibuka.

389
00:26:50,903 --> 00:26:52,071
Jadi, kudengar,

390
00:26:54,031 --> 00:26:56,784
para buruh pabrik mendukungnya.

391
00:26:59,745 --> 00:27:01,664
- Namun, belakangan...
- Mereka menentangnya.

392
00:27:02,248 --> 00:27:04,667
Pabrik itu akan kalah dari bisnis baru.

393
00:27:07,336 --> 00:27:08,337
Pria yang mencoba

394
00:27:08,879 --> 00:27:10,297
membakar dirinya sendiri

395
00:27:11,048 --> 00:27:12,174
ada di foto ini?

396
00:27:13,968 --> 00:27:16,095
- Dia salah satunya?
- Mungkin.

397
00:27:17,763 --> 00:27:18,806
<i>Pengkhianat!</i>

398
00:27:19,056 --> 00:27:20,558
Kim Seung-cheol!

399
00:27:21,017 --> 00:27:24,437
Kau harus minta maaf! Kim Seung-cheol!

400
00:27:25,312 --> 00:27:26,647
- Hentikan.
- Pengkhianat!

401
00:27:27,231 --> 00:27:29,191
- Tenanglah.
- Kim Seung-cheol! Minta maaf!

402
00:27:29,984 --> 00:27:33,029
- Tenang, Pak.
- Minta maaflah!

403
00:27:33,988 --> 00:27:34,822
Padamkan.

404
00:27:34,905 --> 00:27:36,532
Kim Seung-cheol!

405
00:27:36,615 --> 00:27:38,451
Kau harus minta maaf!

406
00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:48,044
Maaf, tapi aku tak tahu.

407
00:27:49,754 --> 00:27:51,338
Aku tak lihat wajahnya.

408
00:27:52,298 --> 00:27:54,675
Ada tulisan Pabrik Beton Songju
di punggungnya.

409
00:27:56,052 --> 00:27:57,511
Kurasa ini seragamnya.

410
00:27:58,179 --> 00:27:59,096
Baiklah.

411
00:28:00,389 --> 00:28:01,932
Akan kuselidiki.

412
00:28:02,975 --> 00:28:04,560
Terima kasih soal ini.

413
00:28:11,650 --> 00:28:12,735
Hampir lupa.

414
00:28:17,156 --> 00:28:18,199
Mengenai suamimu...

415
00:28:19,658 --> 00:28:21,368
Aku tak melihat bukti perselingkuhan.

416
00:28:24,121 --> 00:28:25,206
Setidaknya, belum ada.

417
00:28:26,332 --> 00:28:27,416
Detektif Jo.

418
00:28:29,835 --> 00:28:30,961
Sang-hun...

419
00:28:32,088 --> 00:28:34,006
Tolong temukan dia, kumohon padamu.

420
00:28:37,301 --> 00:28:38,386
Ya.

421
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:40,971
<i>Pria yang mencoba membakar diri</i>

422
00:28:41,806 --> 00:28:43,224
<i>bernama Kim Pil-yeon.</i>

423
00:28:43,641 --> 00:28:45,226
<i>Dia wakil serikat buruh.</i>

424
00:28:45,309 --> 00:28:46,685
<font color="#ffff00">TOKO DAGING</font>

425
00:28:46,769 --> 00:28:48,979
<i>Namun, kami tak bisa menghubunginya.</i>

426
00:28:49,980 --> 00:28:52,817
<i>Kudengar, istrinya punya
toko daging di Songju.</i>

427
00:28:53,526 --> 00:28:54,527
Permisi.

428
00:28:55,694 --> 00:28:56,779
Ada orang?

429
00:29:00,157 --> 00:29:02,243
<font color="#ffff00">DISEWAKAN</font>

430
00:29:03,577 --> 00:29:04,703
Siapa kau?

431
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:10,584
Aku polisi.

432
00:29:11,001 --> 00:29:13,087
Apakah nama suamimu Kim Pil-yeon?

433
00:29:14,296 --> 00:29:16,215
Tunggu di dalam.

434
00:29:23,973 --> 00:29:25,766
Kami akan pindah pekan ini.

435
00:29:26,767 --> 00:29:28,978
Kami mencari suamimu.

436
00:29:29,478 --> 00:29:30,646
Kau tahu di mana dia?

437
00:29:31,439 --> 00:29:33,107
Sudah sepekan aku tak melihatnya.

438
00:29:34,358 --> 00:29:35,443
<i>Sepekan?</i>

439
00:29:35,901 --> 00:29:38,446
<i>Itu saat Kim Seung-cheol tewas
dan Jeong Sang-hun hilang.</i>

440
00:29:39,488 --> 00:29:40,406
Namun,

441
00:29:40,739 --> 00:29:42,158
kelihatannya kau tidak heran.

442
00:29:42,825 --> 00:29:44,535
Polisi mencari suamimu,

443
00:29:44,827 --> 00:29:46,370
tapi kau tak bertanya kenapa.

444
00:29:47,413 --> 00:29:51,750
Bu, jika tahu di mana dia,
tolong beri tahu aku.

445
00:29:51,834 --> 00:29:53,294
Sampaikan padanya jika menemukannya.

446
00:29:56,547 --> 00:29:57,590
Katakan, jangan pulang.

447
00:30:00,217 --> 00:30:01,510
Bahkan setelah mati.

448
00:30:07,141 --> 00:30:09,310
Ibu, aku lapar.

449
00:30:09,393 --> 00:30:11,645
Baik. Tunggu di atas.

450
00:30:20,321 --> 00:30:23,491
<i>Dari potongannya, alat yang dipakai
adalah kapak atau pisau daging.</i>

451
00:30:57,775 --> 00:30:59,652
Jangan makan denganku jika bawa bekal.

452
00:31:00,486 --> 00:31:01,737
Kau sangat aneh.

453
00:31:02,446 --> 00:31:03,697
- Jin-gyeong.
- Ya?

454
00:31:03,781 --> 00:31:04,657
- Kau sibuk?
- Apa?

455
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:07,034
Jika tidak, buka acar lobak itu.

456
00:31:07,117 --> 00:31:08,244
Baik.

457
00:31:08,953 --> 00:31:10,204
Ho-gyu tak sibuk, 'kan?

458
00:31:10,871 --> 00:31:12,206
Lantas apa?

459
00:31:12,289 --> 00:31:13,958
Jeong Sang-hun dan Kim Seung-cheol

460
00:31:14,291 --> 00:31:17,461
tampaknya punya relasi baik
tanpa perselisihan.

461
00:31:17,545 --> 00:31:18,837
Jadi, mereka menginap

462
