di hotel di Songju dan lakukan sesuatu?

463
00:31:20,798 --> 00:31:21,674
Benar.

464
00:31:22,424 --> 00:31:25,010
Aku sama sekali tak mau membayangkannya.

465
00:31:25,094 --> 00:31:25,928
Hei.

466
00:31:27,221 --> 00:31:28,222
