00:31:31,642 --> 00:31:32,810
kerjakan sesuatu bersama.

469
00:31:32,893 --> 00:31:36,480
- Mengerjakan apa?
- Ho-gyu, ambil kertas itu.

470
00:31:36,564 --> 00:31:37,398
Sebentar.

471
00:31:39,733 --> 00:31:40,776
Ini.

472
00:31:41,151 --> 00:31:42,486
Apa ini?

473
00:31:42,861 --> 00:31:47,408
"Relokasi situs bisnis
energi terbarukan Songju"?

474
00:31:48,158 --> 00:31:49,493
Kerja bagus.

475
00:31:49,577 --> 00:31:51,912
Berarti Kim Seung-cheol
mendukung bisnis baru

476
00:31:51,996 --> 00:31:54,290
yang dikerjakan Jeong Sang-hun.

477
00:31:54,373 --> 00:31:57,376
Jadi, apa kaitan bisnis baru itu

478
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,295
dengan Kim Pil-yeon?

479
00:31:59,378 --> 00:32:01,714
Astaga, kurasa kau sama sekali

