481
00:32:04,842 --> 00:32:05,718
Begini.

482
00:32:05,801 --> 00:32:09,138
Siapa yang menciptakan pekerjaan
dengan membangun pabrik di sini?

483
00:32:09,388 --> 00:32:10,556
Kim Seung-cheol.

484
00:32:11,223 --> 00:32:14,768
Bagi Kim Pil-yeon,
dia bukan hanya anggota majelis.

485
00:32:14,852 --> 00:32:16,103
Dia adalah idola.

486
00:32:16,186 --> 00:32:18,522
Idola. Panutan.

487
00:32:19,106 --> 00:32:21,650
Namun, masalah mulai timbul

488
00:32:21,734 --> 00:32:23,319
karena satu pria.

489
00:32:23,569 --> 00:32:24,612
Siapa menurutmu?

490
00:32:24,945 --> 00:32:26,196
Jeong Sang-hun.

491
00:32:26,363 --> 00:32:28,949
Dia mengumumkan penutupan pabrik

492
00:32:29,033 --> 00:32:31,160
dan memulai bisnis baru di sana.

493
00:32:31,410 --> 00:32:33,954
Kim Seung-cheol yang dipercayai buruh

494
00:32:34,038 --> 00:32:35,205
malah memihak Sang-hun.

495
00:32:35,289 --> 00:32:38,250
Kim Pil-yeon menggila
dan menemui Kim Seung-cheol.

496
00:32:38,334 --> 00:32:39,877
Dia membakar diri sendiri

497
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:42,588
untuk bunuh diri, tapi gagal.

498
00:32:43,922 --> 00:32:46,717
Jika diperhatikan baik-baik,

499
00:32:47,968 --> 00:32:49,595
Jeong Sang-hun sangat tampan.

500
00:32:49,887 --> 00:32:50,971
Dia juga kaya.

501
00:32:52,056 --> 00:32:54,767
Kim Pil-yeon menjadi iri.

502
00:32:55,809 --> 00:32:57,311
Dia memutuskan menghancurkan

503
00:32:57,394 --> 00:32:59,355
dan membunuh mereka semua!

504
00:32:59,438 --> 00:33:00,481
Jin-gyeong!

505
00:33:02,608 --> 00:33:04,026
Kapan ceritamu selesai?

506
00:33:04,109 --> 00:33:05,486
Biar kujelaskan lagi.

507
00:33:05,569 --> 00:33:07,529
Mertua dan menantu bekerja sama

508
00:33:07,613 --> 00:33:08,697
untuk menutup pabrik

509
00:33:08,781 --> 00:33:10,324
dan membuka bisnis baru.

510
00:33:10,532 --> 00:33:13,744
Karena itu Kim Pil-yeon
dendam pada mereka.

511
00:33:13,827 --> 00:33:15,412
- Begitu.
- Itu yang kukatakan.

512
00:33:15,496 --> 00:33:18,040
Sama sekali berbeda.

513
00:33:18,457 --> 00:33:20,709
Astaga, itu kejam.

514
00:33:21,919 --> 00:33:24,797
Kurasa Jin-gyeong suka mengarang.

515
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,215
Itu penyakit.

516
00:33:26,298 --> 00:33:28,050
Hei, hentikan.

517
00:33:28,133 --> 00:33:30,719
Kalian harus dengarkan aku.

518
00:33:30,803 --> 00:33:31,762
<font color="#ffff00">HASIL TES</font>

519
00:33:31,845 --> 00:33:33,180
<font color="#ffff00">COCOK</font>

520
00:33:34,306 --> 00:33:35,599
Kapten.

521
00:33:36,925 --> 00:33:38,010
Mereka menemukannya.

522
00:33:38,135 --> 00:33:39,136
Apa?

523
00:33:40,679 --> 00:33:42,139
DNA Jeong Sang-hun.

524
00:33:42,598 --> 00:33:44,516
Ditemukan di salah satu pisau itu.

525
00:33:49,796 --> 00:33:53,133
<i>Polisi yakin wakil serikat buruh
Pabrik Beton Songju</i>

526
00:33:53,216 --> 00:33:55,844
<i>adalah tersangka penculik
Jeong Sang-hun dari Grup JQ</i>

527
00:33:55,927 --> 00:33:57,512
<i>dan sedang memburunya.</i>

528
00:33:57,646 --> 00:33:59,439
<i>Silakan, Reporter Jeong Hyeon-cheol.</i>

529
00:34:00,482 --> 00:34:03,485
<i>Polisi menemukan pisau
dengan darah Dirut Jeong</i>

530
00:34:03,568 --> 00:34:06,029
<i>di toko daging milik istri Kim.</i>

531
00:34:06,113 --> 00:34:07,781
<i>Pabrik tempat Kim bekerja</i>

532
00:34:07,864 --> 00:34:10,325
<i>akan segera ditutup</i>

533
00:34:10,408 --> 00:34:12,702
<i>karena bisnis energi terbarukan Grup JQ,</i>

534
00:34:12,786 --> 00:34:14,788
<i>mungkin ini yang jadi alasan kejahatannya.</i>

535
00:34:14,871 --> 00:34:17,541
<i>Kim masuk daftar buron di seluruh negeri.</i>

536
00:34:18,041 --> 00:34:20,502
<i>Berdasarkan situasi, mungkin Kim terlibat</i>

537
00:34:20,535 --> 00:34:21,953
<i>dalam kematian Kim Seung-cheol.</i>

538
00:34:22,037 --> 00:34:23,914
<i>Polisi pun sedang menyelidiki hal ini.</i>

539
00:35:09,084 --> 00:35:09,960
Ada apa?

540
00:35:37,154 --> 00:35:38,321
Pria...

541
00:35:40,198 --> 00:35:42,617
yang ditemui Sang-hun terakhir kali.

542
00:35:43,577 --> 00:35:45,412
Kau menemukan Kim Pil-yeon?

543
00:35:45,787 --> 00:35:47,956
Maaf, Pak. Kami mencarinya ke mana-mana.

544
00:35:48,039 --> 00:35:51,251
Kenapa lama sekali menemukannya?

545
00:35:53,753 --> 00:35:56,298
Polisi sedang memburunya.

546
00:35:56,882 --> 00:35:58,508
Kita akan segera temukan dia.

547
00:35:58,717 --> 00:35:59,676
Maaf, Pak Jeong.

548
00:35:59,759 --> 00:36:02,554
Ini semua berawal karenamu.

549
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:05,056
Ingat ini.

550
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:07,851
Jika Sang-hun tidak kembali,

551
00:36:08,393 --> 00:36:10,478
tak akan ada tempat

552
00:36:12,439 --> 00:36:13,857
bagimu di sini.

553
00:36:14,149 --> 00:36:15,150
Paham?

554
00:36:15,734 --> 00:36:16,943
Keluar!

555
00:36:36,421 --> 00:36:38,298
PABRIK BETON SONGJU, DIRUT CHOI CHI-DEUK

556
00:36:38,882 --> 00:36:40,091
Kim Pil-yeon?

557
00:36:40,508 --> 00:36:42,177
Aku tak tahu banyak tentang dia.

558
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:44,137
Namun, dia wakil serikat buruh.

559
00:36:44,221 --> 00:36:46,473
Itu sebabnya aku tak kenal.
Kami tidak berteman.

560
00:36:47,557 --> 00:36:50,227
Namun, bukan berarti kami bermusuhan.

561
00:36:50,310 --> 00:36:53,313
Kami bukan teman atau musuh.

562
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,898
Itu maksudku.

563
00:36:55,148 --> 00:36:57,442
Kira-kira, di mana dia?

564
00:36:58,443 --> 00:36:59,402
Entahlah.

565
00:36:59,945 --> 00:37:02,030
Kurasa dia pernah terlihat di kasino.

566
00:37:02,697 --> 00:37:04,199
Namun, aku tak tahu apa pun.

567
00:37:05,325 --> 00:37:07,410
Tanyalah para anggota serikat.

568
00:37:08,536 --> 00:37:09,496
Silakan minum.

569
00:37:09,579 --> 00:37:13,208
Ini teh kunyit.
Sangat baik bagi kesehatan.

570
00:37:15,252 --> 00:37:18,588
- Halo.
- Sial. Tak ada yang bisa jawab telepon?

571
00:37:20,465 --> 00:37:22,342
Hei, kerja bagus.

572
00:37:22,801 --> 00:37:24,469
- Kau temukan sesuatu?
- Tidak.

573
00:37:24,552 --> 00:37:27,222
Kuperiksa semua kamera keamanan
di sekitar sana,

574
00:37:27,305 --> 00:37:28,932
tapi Jeong Sang-hun lenyap

575
00:37:29,015 --> 00:37:30,183
sejak dari kedai teh.

576
00:37:30,267 --> 00:37:32,102
Seperti mencari hantu.

577
00:37:32,519 --> 00:37:33,645
Tae-sik, bagaimana kau?

578
00:37:33,728 --> 00:37:34,938
Menemukan sesuatu?

579
00:37:35,021 --> 00:37:36,481
- Halo?
- Dirut dan anggota serikat

580
00:37:36,564 --> 00:37:38,733
tak bicara banyak tentang Kim Pil-yeon.

581
00:37:38,817 --> 00:37:40,986
Adakah laporan yang membantu?

582
00:37:41,069 --> 00:37:43,655
Hanya sejumlah telepon iseng. Sial.

583
00:37:43,738 --> 00:37:46,283
Ponselnya mati, tak bisa dilacak.

584
00:37:46,366 --> 00:37:48,702
- Di mana dia bersembunyi?
- Kau pasti kaget.

585
00:37:50,161 --> 00:37:52,080
Siapa namamu tadi?

586
00:37:52,956 --> 00:37:55,125
- Halo.
- Jeongseon, Provinsi Gangwon.

587
00:37:56,209 --> 00:37:59,879
Entah. Kurasa dia
pernah terlihat di kasino.

588
00:38:00,005 --> 00:38:01,840
- Aku dengar.
- Jeongseon, Provinsi Gangwon.

589
00:38:01,923 --> 00:38:03,675
Berikan padaku.

590
00:38:03,758 --> 00:38:05,635
- Kau melihat Kim Seung-cheol?
- Tunggu.

591
00:38:06,136 --> 00:38:07,554
Dia sudah meninggal.

592
00:38:07,887 --> 00:38:09,055
- Ya?
- Halo?

593
00:38:09,139 --> 00:38:11,391
- Halo?
- Alamatnya?

594
