Entahlah. Aku tak tahu...

601
00:40:35,118 --> 00:40:36,703
Di mana Jeong Sang-hun sembunyi?

602
00:40:36,828 --> 00:40:38,538
Aku tak tahu, Keparat!

603
00:40:57,223 --> 00:40:58,308
Kau tak mau bilang?

604
00:41:00,310 --> 00:41:01,186
Aku tak tahu!

605
00:41:11,154 --> 00:41:12,155
Sial.

606
00:41:33,635 --> 00:41:34,969
Hei!

607
00:41:36,846 --> 00:41:37,805
Seo-hui.

608
00:41:38,848 --> 00:41:39,891
Ayah Mertua.

609
00:41:46,481 --> 00:41:49,651
Astaga. Kenapa bepergian sendirian
saat hujan?

610
00:41:52,737 --> 00:41:54,364
Kau pasti sangat sedih.

611
00:41:55,949 --> 00:41:57,450
Tak bisa kubayangkan.

612
00:41:58,076 --> 00:41:59,827
Bahkan aku pun merasa tertekan.

613
00:41:59,911 --> 00:42:01,788
Kau pasti putus asa.

614
00:42:05,124 --> 00:42:06,459
Aku melihat berita itu.

615
00:42:08,044 --> 00:42:09,212
Ayah Mertua.

616
00:42:12,090 --> 00:42:14,884
Bagaimana orang bisa setega itu?

617
00:42:18,596 --> 00:42:20,098
Hanya karena alasan itu...

618
00:42:23,017 --> 00:42:24,227
Bagaimana bisa orang lakukan itu?

619
00:42:25,687 --> 00:42:27,564
Kau dibutakan satu hal yang hilang,

620
00:42:27,855 --> 00:42:30,525
padahal punya 100 hal lain, itu manusiawi.

621
00:42:31,859 --> 00:42:32,694
Aku mengerti.

622
00:42:34,070 --> 00:42:35,863
Bahkan aku pun sulit percaya

623
00:42:36,239 --> 00:42:37,615
saat menyadari kenyataan.

624
00:42:41,244 --> 00:42:42,579
Maafkan aku, Ayah Mertua.

625
00:42:45,498 --> 00:42:46,874
Ayah Mertua, maafkan aku.

626
00:42:49,711 --> 00:42:52,755
Di hari terakhir bertemu dengan Sang-hun,

627
00:42:54,549 --> 00:42:57,260
aku bersikap sangat kasar padanya.

628
00:43:00,763 --> 00:43:03,266
Bagaimana jika aku
tak pernah melihatnya lagi?

629
00:43:05,184 --> 00:43:06,185
Tidak.

630
00:43:06,894 --> 00:43:08,521
Itu tak akan terjadi.

631
00:43:09,439 --> 00:43:10,565
Aku tahu

632
00:43:10,648 --> 00:43:12,442
Sang-hun akan kembali.

633
00:43:13,151 --> 00:43:14,068
Pasti.

634
00:43:20,908 --> 00:43:22,702
Dia pasti akan kembali,

635
00:43:23,161 --> 00:43:24,495
jadi, jangan cemas.

636
00:43:25,330 --> 00:43:26,956
- Ya?
- Baik.

637
00:43:52,273 --> 00:43:53,566
Sang-hun.

638
00:43:59,364 --> 00:44:00,990
Hei, Sang-hun!

639
00:44:01,074 --> 00:44:02,950
Sang-hun!

640
00:44:10,583 --> 00:44:12,251
Kau jadi berat.

641
00:44:13,461 --> 00:44:14,712
Hei!

642
00:44:17,215 --> 00:44:19,008
Kau dari mana?

643
00:44:19,300 --> 00:44:20,301
Katakan!

644
00:44:20,802 --> 00:44:22,553
Aku sangat gelisah menunggumu.

645
00:44:23,054 --> 00:44:25,640
Kenapa tidak jawab telepon?

646
00:44:25,723 --> 00:44:28,351
Kenapa begitu padaku? Kau dari mana?

647
00:44:28,810 --> 00:44:30,603
Dasar bodoh.

648
00:44:32,355 --> 00:44:35,983
- Maafkan aku.
- Aku putus asa menunggumu.

