00:44:42,657 --> 00:44:45,243
Aku juga, Sang-hun.

652
00:44:45,326 --> 00:44:46,744
Aku sangat merindukanmu.

653
00:44:49,872 --> 00:44:51,124
Biar kulihat.

654
00:44:52,208 --> 00:44:53,334
Baik-baik saja?

655
00:44:55,086 --> 00:44:56,337
Kau tak apa-apa?

656
00:45:03,177 --> 00:45:04,804
Aku sangat lega.

657
00:45:05,221 --> 00:45:06,848
Syukurlah kau kembali.

658
00:46:19,837 --> 00:46:20,838
Sang-hun...

